social_posts.post_text:
What a great #nyfw show! I love collaborating with @marrisawilsonny 
It was a magical moment in 2022 for all my artist family to come together to bring life to her collection!!! 

Can’t wait for 2023!!!!!

@kevynaucoin @purplepr @brandon_montoya_nyc @brandon_mua_nyc @lijhajade @iamolga @melikokoro @makeupbydita @starr_ceska @eddieartistry @brushedbyceliaaurora @oribe

I AM OBSESSED WITH THIS BRUSH!!!!!
I helped to design this brush and wanted to create a foundation application tool that makes my applications easier.
One side is like using your finger to apply, and the other side is like using your favorite sponge to bounce, blend and buff your foundation to perfection!!!
I use multiple Duet Foundation Brushes for cream/liquid contour, highlight and blusher application!

#yourbeautyisbrave #teamkevyn #artistbrushseries @kevynaucoin #etherealistfoundation

I love a 3-D juicy #glazed #liplook 
Use a flesh tone lip liner as a base (Divine)
Contour with a neutral beige/brown (New Naked)
Top with a nude lipstick (Thelmadora)
Finish with a glaze of gloss (Prism Rose)

#teamkevyn #yourbeautyisbrave @kevynaucoin #glassglowlip #unforgettablelipdefiner #unforgettablelipstick @glamourbydrita #dritaslipkit

SIMPLIFY CONCEALER APPLICATIONS
I love applying just enough concealer and corrector to balance and brighten in a natural way. 
This brush is a staple in my kit for many reasons. 
Love it for concealing, lip application and shadow application. The synthetic fibers make it perfect for creams, liquids and powders.

#duetconcealerbrush #artistbrishseries #teamkevyn #kevynaucoin #kevynaucoinbeauty #yourbeautyisbrave @kevynaucoin @beautyfashionsales

Daily brush cleaning is a must!!! Especially between makeup clients. 
I am in love with the new @cinemasecretspro formula!!!!!
Dip, wipe, dry!!

#teamkevyn #kevynaucoin #brushcleaner #artistbrushseries #yourbeautyisbrave @kevynaucoin @beautyfashionsales @cinemasecretspro @themakeupshow

DEEP CLEANSE YOUR PERSONAL MAKEUP BRUSHES!!!
Try a shampoo conditioner combo!
The conditioner helps break down product! 
I love lathering my brushes up!

#teamkevyn #artistbrushseries #yourbeautyisbrave @kevynaucoin @themakeupshow @thepowdergroup @beautyfashionsales @shopriotbeauty

Always an incredible experience working with @marrisawilsonny and @oribe for #nyfw 
This collection was inspired by Marrisa’s connection with dance, movement and jazz. 
The dream artistry team brought these makeups to life!!!!
And yes! I got to work with the most beautiful human @patcleveland 
What an iconic moment!
February 11, 2023 is marked as one of my favorite experiences!

@kevynaucoin #teamkevyn #teamoribe @oribepro @kienhoang #yourbeautyisbrave #artistbrushseries

Backstage magic with @cucculellishaheen for the Les Radiants Collection 15.
Darkness and light, chaos and classicism.

It was such a pleasure collaborating with the designers and seeing the looks come to life with the #dreamteam of makeup artists.

LOOSE POWDER & BRONZER APPLICATION. 
A fluffy powder brush is the best tool for applying your loose and pressed setting powders as well as the best tool for applying bronzer evenly.
Try the new @kevynaucoin blurring powder brush!!!

#yourbeautyisbrave #artistbrushseries #kevynaucoin

I love me some #indecentlashes 
for MAXIMUM VOLUME & DEPTH 
Start by filling in the lash line with a dark pencil.
Then add a wing with your favorite liquid liner.
ALWAYS CURL (even if you have curly lashes, this grooms your lashes in the same direction)
APPLY #indecentmascara 

Liner: Precision Eye Definer
Liquid Liner: Precision Liquid Liner
@kevynaucoin Lash Curler
Mascara: Indecent Mascara 
 
#teamkevyn #yourbeautyisbrave #lashapplication

The gorgeous @emichew for @themakeupshow 
So excited for Chicago, New York and Nashville!!!!

Hope to see you @themakeupshow I will be there with @shopriotbeauty 

Products: @kevynaucoin 
-NEW Artist Brush Series
-stripped Nude Skin Tint 
-Sensual Skin Enhancer
-Neo Blush
-Contour Book 3.0
-Glass Glow Face
-Lip Definer
-Glass Glow Lip

@anastasiabeverlyhills black gel eyeliner

@danessa_myricks New Blurring Powder Flushed Blush

SCULPTING MADE EASY

I love the new Duet Contour Brush (Apply, Flip, Buff)

This brush works with creams , liquids and powders. 
The smaller brush head is perfect for enhancing shadows and the larger brush is perfect for blending and buffing.

Cream contour first with Sensual Skin Enhancer, set with powder, the enhance contours with Contour Powder.
#yourbeautyisbrave #teamkevyn @kevynaucoin #artistbrushseries 
@shopriotbeauty 
@beautyfashionsales

WHEN WINTER WON’T QUIT!

Still snowing so let’s play with a “just in from the cold” glowing look!

PRO TIP: mix a drop of Glass Glow Face into your cream or liquid foundation, before applying.

Finish with a drop of Glass Glow Face mixed with your favorite blush to create a glass blush look.

PRODUCTS USED:
-Sensual Skin Primer
-Glass Glow Face, Pixie Dream
-Neo Blush, Rosecliff
-Loose Setting Powder

This Duet Blush Brush is everything!
I use it for Powder, Blush, Sculpting, Highlight and all around blending! 
I have to have this in my personal & professional kits.
Two perfect sizes of brush heads for detail work and for creating beautiful washes of color!!!

@kevynaucoin #artistbrushseries #teamkevyn #yourbeautyisbrave

I’m so EXCITED for these! They are a long time coming. I’m so proud to be a part of the team that designed these, taking inspirations from @kevynaucoin and his iconic methods of sculpt, highlight and blush. These formulas are so smooth and blend beautifully!!! Wait till you try the glazy texture of the highlights ! #teamkevyn #kevynaucoinbeauty #kevynaucoin #sculpting #beautybelongstoeveryone

Round 1 of Deep pore cleansing on @bagabon 
Follow @the.sugar.xaddy for my journey as an esthetician and to see progress on my clients skin.

@christinevalmy oily acne skin treatments are amazing!!! 
Love Special Lotion 22 after a full deep pore facial with lots of extractions. 

#thesugarxaddy #facialtreatment #facialmassage #deepporecleansing #extractions

Happy Halloween Season!! 
I am@in love with my new @esumcosmetics Artistry Pigment Palette and Illustrator Precision Pen Line

#batman #halloweenmakeup #venetianmask #masquerade #halloween #esum

Ombré Powder Brows technique on my lovely esthe friend @glamorousglowesthetics for my certification with @browsbyannazong 

She wakes up this way!!! Can’t wait to see her for a touch up in a few weeks. 

Ombré powder brows lasts 1-3 years. Witch touch up, they can’t for a long long time! 

After healing the color softens and leaves you with a gorgeous everyday brow slay!!!!

#wakeupwithmakeup #powderbrows #pmu #pmuartist  @browsbyannazong @christinevalmy

Happy Halloween and Dia De Los Muertos!
Bringing this creation to life using all beauty makeup items. No need to invest in special FX when you can create with your everyday incredible items from @esumcosmetics 
I am in love with the Artistry Palettes and the Pen Liner.

The new Artistry Palette No.4 has incredible highlighter options for your face and eyes! 

#halloween #halloweenmakeup #sugarskull #diadelosmuertos #halfskullmakeup

Another alien superstar muse @itstiky for @themakeupshow 

I guess colorful aliens is my theme this year for #halloween 

Catch me at @themakeupshow in all location for 2024. I would love to see you and share some of my techniques for all the incredible educations and seminars.
#seeyouatthenakeupshow @themakeupshow #themakeupshow #makeupshow #makeup #alien #alienmakeup 

📸 @anluis
